                <span class="text-xs bg-peach/20 text-peach px-2 py-0.5 rounded"
                  >Snapshots</span
                >
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-subtext0 mb-4">
              Create and restore system snapshots with Timeshift or Snapper.
              Automatic scheduling keeps your system protected.
            </p>
          </div>
