        </h2>
        <p class="text-subtext0 text-lg mb-12">
          Every tool in Aegis is built with the same principles
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div>
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">üé®</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-text mb-2">Consistent Theming</h3>
            <p class="text-subtext0 text-sm">
              All apps use Catppuccin Mocha colors and follow Libadwaita design
              patterns
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">‚ö°</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-text mb-2">Native Performance</h3>
            <p class="text-subtext0 text-sm">
              Built with Python and GTK4, not Electron. Fast startup and minimal
              resource usage
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">üîß</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-text mb-2">CLI Under the Hood</h3>
            <p class="text-subtext0 text-sm">
              GUIs wrap powerful CLI tools. You can always drop to terminal for
              more control
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="px-4 py-16">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text mb-4">
          Tools That Respect Your Time
        </h2>
        <p class="text-subtext0 text-lg mb-8">
          Download Aegis and experience system tools done right.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/download"
          class="inline-block bg-peach hover:bg-yellow text-crust font-semibold px-10 py-4 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200 text-xl"
        >
          Download Now
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
